    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors accepted at gradation 1 per MRL 2 scoping. Validation results for pressure head, velocity field, and wall shear stress demonstrate adequate agreement with experimental data. The RH index sweep confirms all operating points satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Aleatory uncertainty from donor RBC fragility variability is acknowledged in the assessment narrative and judged to be bounded by the applied safety margin. The overall body of evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for this Class II CPB device.",
